{"tid":1540504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係九龍灣整緊連儂牆，有位叔叔同我講","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:26:44.000Z","uid":69276,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eeffb2abc8e672ffef4ca3d2cfa792cf997bb3bd","tid":1540504,"uid":69276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"大約6點半左右，係我準備貼五大訴求嘅字句果陣身邊有幾位叔叔係度吹水，之後其中一位行埋黎我身邊同我講:五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n之後有一位又教我貼係咩位置好d，又有一位去買d文具翻黎補充，之後開始愈黎愈多人一齊整連儂牆。我想係度多謝果幾叔叔同埋一齊貼連儂牆嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，絕不袋住先<br />\n香港人，保持堅毅<br />\n我地一定要堅持落去直到爭取到真正嘅民主自由<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油。"},{"pid":"3bd9b10e3b7681834cc0276bb4a7833463ef1ee4","tid":1540504,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Yt9JA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7Yt9JA.jpg&h=c1d70329&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4okoYBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4okoYBW.jpg&h=be2da638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a6ea7d0f3ea415df5cfae7af7f7b306221202ad","tid":1540504,"uid":318028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4b3adb0726f3d2aae557e5b2b246b4e6a2dd46","tid":1540504,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:52:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第六訴求</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Yt9JA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7Yt9JA.jpg&h=c1d70329&s={SIZE}\"